                  <br /><br />
                <a href="https://symplifica.com/" style="text-decoration:none;width: 90%;display:block;margin: 0 auto;" target="_blank;"><div style="background:#13878e;border-radius:25px; height: 25px; font-size:14px; width: 170px; color:#FFFFFF;font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; padding: 5px 0 0 0; text-align:center">Ir a Symplifica</div></a><br /><br />
